  "name": "RPlog_Fleming_s_Reinsertion_Plan",
  "title": "Fleming's Reinsertion Plan",
  "summary": "Aboard the Star Destroyer Predator, ISB Sector Director Korynn Fleming, deliberately disheveled and bearing self-inflicted lash marks, prepares a scheme to be reinserted into the Imperial Security Bureau as a secret Sith agent. He consults Darth Malign, who approves the plan and praises Fleming's clinical, art-like devotion, then dispatches Captains Dareus and Axel Vichten to assist while voicing his anger at the missing Lynae Cassius, whose medical research Fleming intends to exploit. Over breakfast and caf on the observation deck, the three men refine the operation: Fleming will be staged as the victim of a botched mercenary interrogation, encased in carbonite, slipped into the cargo of an unwitting CSA-registered smuggler with falsified manifests, and 'discovered' by his own ISB agents, who will burn a false trail framing others. Axel arranges the smuggler, freezing facility, and scanner trigger, while Dareus insists on shadowing the shipment with untraceable Sith assassin droids over Axel's objections. The plan settled, the men disperse to set it in motion, Fleming bracing for the dangerous carbon-freeze.",
